	before comparing with GDBM_READER.
	Support GDBM_CLOEXEC.
	(dbm_open): Translate O_CLOEXEC to GDBM_CLOEXEC.

	* doc/gdbm.texinfo: Document GDBM_CLOEXEC.
	
